data.description: This immaculate home is a four bedroom, two bath home immaculately designed with those extra touches. Boasting spacious bedrooms that allow for optional furniture arrangement, the open concept living/dining with drop lighting over a granite topped island is a chef's dream and gives a nice ambiance in the evening while multiple windows bring plenty of natural light during the day. Ample cabinets for storage space and walk in pantry make this kitchen a chef's dream. Primary bedroom sits towards the back with its en-suite bath, double vanity and walk in closet. With features such as a smart thermostat to lock doors and set temperature while away. The large backyard and prime location in a sought after neighborhood, offers comfort and convenience as it is less than ten minutes to the entertainment and shops or our famous Belton Lake activities. BISD bus stops on same block. This is truly a property to not miss out on.
